{"tid":2214483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"潘曉穎父母要求陳同佳盡快投案 管浩鳴：等我下星期和同佳見面後再回覆大家","createTime":"2020-09-23T09:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T11:23:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7506a69940f34c29753d5344f914946616bab2d0","tid":2214483,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:36:37.000Z","msg":"台灣殺人案女死者潘曉穎的父母透過網媒《立場新聞》，向涉案疑犯陳同佳發公開信，要求陳同佳親自回應何時會到台灣自首，並質疑他「龜縮」。一直跟進事件的聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴表示，下星期會與陳同佳會面。<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒在手機通訊群組向管浩鳴查詢，陳同佳會否考慮答應潘曉穎父母要求赴台自首或自設期限，並承諾於限期前赴台；以及對於潘曉穎父母指台灣早已開通「特別聯繫窗口」，隨時準備讓陳同佳投案，質疑陳同佳為何要龜縮，詢問陳同佳或管浩鳴，對此有何回應。<br />\n<br />\n管浩鳴回應說，待他與陳同佳會面後，再回覆傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551214-20200923.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551214-20200923.htm&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9j11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=74cb8bd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551214-20200923.htm&h=400b89a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551214-20200923.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f4d6a299c4ed2751b53613dc6b4bfb2546fb7c64","tid":2214483,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e2a51f24fe83ce5ec2c6c5d6ab63965810030f","tid":2214483,"uid":7482,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佳佳:我憑實力帶你個女去台灣再無穿無爛番香港<br />\n點解要我自首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a3f5da24c1b93014bba37d0cc5defd02855b0f","tid":2214483,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"落雨 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432b56cd0c56e0305f694b50e98d2